{"tid":439305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】東鐵列車影裙底 紅褲男跑7卡氣咳被擒","createTime":"2017-10-17T16:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T14:31:28.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bd3ee9f6eb54e4b313c755000e840693f14d5533","tid":439305,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171017/57341295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171017%2F57341295&d=%2BStmu2oD2BmvbffMkvJrmcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0c720d18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171017%2F57341295&h=f10e50f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171017/57341295</a><br />\n<br />\n清晨約6時，一名26歲身穿短裙女子，乘搭港鐵東鐵綫北上，當列車由大學站駛往大埔墟站時，她發現一名男乘客用手機偷拍其裙底，即時大叫求助。<br />\n其時一名港鐵男職員同樣乘車上班途中，身處同一車廂(第9卡)，聽到呼叫上前協助。涉案男乘客拔足往車頭方向逃跑，跑到第2卡時疑氣力不繼，被該職員及當值職員合力截獲，再通知車長及大埔墟站職員報警。<br />\n據知有人被制服時，企圖刪除手機相片，但被制止。警員到場調查，以涉嫌遊蕩拘捕該名姓朱37歲男子，拘捕帶署調查。疑犯當時身穿T裇、短褲和涼鞋。<br />\n根據鐵路警區公布的數字，偷拍裙底的舉報數字由2011年至2016年增加55%，由78宗增加至121宗。港鐵去年錄升幅最多的罪案，第二位為偷拍裙底，去年共有121宗，較前年的96宗上升兩成六，連同今年首季的24宗同類個案，警方合共拘捕131人，犯案者年齡介乎17至60歲，他們多以智能手機在自動電梯偷拍，或將偷拍裝置收藏於手提袋或波鞋內。"},{"pid":"43fd75bdf63fcf267a1a435275c1919ddc0c5d10","tid":439305,"uid":1910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"跑黎做乜尻，車門閂左咪一樣俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd239c8cd96dac31963c22c6c980b1740a79f75d","tid":439305,"uid":29514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"跑7卡車既時間都del唔到張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7641340279531aa1438e0d0abec914b5faab54","tid":439305,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"睇佢段片 坐係到影咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁都唔得？"},{"pid":"f8615f2a1a140f166161b6b5ac60896dd8ba4d30","tid":439305,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c00d88910fe13496d352ca0c11b2e3b4156368d","tid":439305,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}